Sentencas: We have fabricated BaCe0.8Gd0.2O3-delta (BCGO) thin films with thickness in the range of 5-10 mu m over substrates composed of Ce0.8Gd0.2O1.9 (CGO)-NiO using a colloidal spray deposition method.
Titulo: High-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells using thin proton-conducting electrolyte with novel cathode

Sentencas: A perovskite-type BaZr0.2Co0.4Fe0.4O3-delta (EZCFO) was employed as a novel cathode material.
Titulo: High-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells using thin proton-conducting electrolyte with novel cathode

Sentencas: The performances of solid oxide fuel cells were investigated from 450 degrees C to 600 degrees C.
Titulo: High-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells using thin proton-conducting electrolyte with novel cathode

Sentencas: The fuel cell with the BCGO film of 9 mu m in thickness showed maximum power outputs of 237, 192, 136 and 89 mW cm(-2) at 600, 550, 500 and 450 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: High-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells using thin proton-conducting electrolyte with novel cathode

Sentencas: The impedance measurements at open circuit conditions showed the polarization resistances of the electrode were about 0.25 and 1.00 Omega cm(2) at 600 and 500 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: High-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells using thin proton-conducting electrolyte with novel cathode

Sentencas: The low interfacial resistances indicated that the BZCFO was a promising cathode material for low-temperature proton-conducing solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: High-performance low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells using thin proton-conducting electrolyte with novel cathode
